  <brief_title>Clinical Trial Examining the Short and Long-term Effect of Myofascial Trigger Points Injection in Low Back Pain Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomized, Double-blind, Clinical Trial of Trigger Point Injection Therapy for the Treatment of Myofascial Pain Syndrome</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Dr. Yoram Shir</agency>
