  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to examine the short and long-term effect of myofascial
      trigger point injections with either a local anesthetic or saline in patients with chronic
      low back pain presenting with myofasical pain syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
